id\"]\n\n<h1>About the Golden Fleece Trading Company</h1>\n\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\"][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"INtro\" background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\"]\n\nThe Golden Fleece Trading Company is owned and run by Larry and Juliette Leighton, who trade directly with quality artisans in Morocco to offer you the opportunity to experience the vibrance of colour and form that these people create.\n\n[/et_pb_text][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Merch text\" background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\"]\n\nWe trade in:\n<ul>\n 	<li>Henna lamps</li>\n 	<li>Brass lanterns</li>\n 	<li>Mirrors</li>\n 	<li>Seagrass baskets and stools</li>\n 	<li>Furniture</li>\n 	<li>Leather pouffes</li>\n 	<li>Babouches and bags</li>\n 	<li>Silk and wool throws and cushions</li>\n 	<li>Safi pottery</li>\n 	<li>Tagines</li>\n<li>Carpets</li>\n<li>Hand-beaten metal sinks</li>\n<li>Handmade mosaic tables</li>\n</ul>\n\nWe also sell a range of sheepskin rugs, deer and goatskins, cow hides and parchement.\n\nIn buying these items you are helping to keep alive age-old traditions, which we support in a modest way in our endeavours to develop fair-trade relationships between artisans and consumers.\n\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\"][et_pb_image admin_label=\"Golden Fleece Trading Company\" src=\"http://gft.tthtesting.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/21435711473_b822393248_k.jpg\" alt=\"Golden Fleece Trading Company\" show_in_lightbox=\"off\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_overlay=\"off\" animation=\"off\" sticky=\"off\" align=\"left\" force_fullwidth=\"off\" always_center_on_mobile=\"on\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" title_text=\"Golden Fleece Trading Company\"]\n\n\n\n[/et_pb_image][et_pb_image admin_