dule_id=\"artisans\"][et_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\"][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Title: Artisans\" background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\"]\n\n<h1>Artisans</h1>\n\n[/et_pb_text][et_pb_gallery admin_label=\"Gallery: artisans\" fullwidth=\"off\" show_title_and_caption=\"off\" show_pagination=\"off\" background_layout=\"light\" auto=\"off\" hover_overlay_color=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.9)\" caption_all_caps=\"off\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" gallery_ids=\"159,164,167,156\"]\n\n\n\n[/et_pb_gallery][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section admin_label=\"Section\" fullwidth=\"on\" specialty=\"off\" background_image=\"http://gft.tthtesting.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/full-width-desert-1.jpg\" transparent_background=\"off\" background_color=\"#ffffff\" allow_player_pause=\"off\" inner_shadow=\"on\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"off\" padding_mobile=\"off\" make_fullwidth=\"off\" use_custom_width=\"off\" width_unit=\"on\" make_equal=\"off\" use_custom_gutter=\"off\" module_class=\"divider-img\"][et_pb_fullwidth_image admin_label=\"Image: desert\" show_in_lightbox=\"off\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_overlay=\"off\" animation=\"fade_in\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" custom_margin=\"7em|0px|7em|0px\"]\n\n\n\n[/et_pb_fullwidth_image][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section admin_label=\"Section\" fullwidth=\"off\" specialty=\"off\" transparent_background=\"off\" background_color=\"#ffffff\" allow_player_pause=\"off\" inner_shadow=\"off\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"off\" padding_mobile=\"off\" make_fullwidth=\"off\" use_custom_width=\"off\" width_unit=\"on\" make_equal=\"off\" use_custom_gutter=\"off\" module_id=\"journeys\"][et_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\"][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Title: Journeys of a Lifetime\" background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\"]\n\n<h1>Journeys of a Lifetime</h1>\n\n[/et_pb_text][et_pb_gallery admin_label=\"Gallery: journeys\" fullwidth=\"off\" show_title_and_caption=\"off\" show_pagination=\"off\" background_layout=\"light\" auto=\"off\" hover_overlay_color=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.9)\" caption_all_caps=\"off\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" gallery_ids=\"217,211,213,218,212,215,214,216\" posts_number=\"8\"]\n\n\n\n[/et_pb_gallery][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\"][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Journeys text 1\" background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\"]\n\nThe Journeys Of a Life-Time are small-group adventures organised by Larry and Juliette with the aim of going a step deeper into Moroccan life than \'normal\' tourism, tasting more of the colour, vibrance and spice that the people there emanate and resound into their environment. The aim is to give each participant the opportunity to dip \'under the skin\' of what they meet, have sufficient space to breathe this in and digest it.\n\nThe idea for our journeys originally flowered from the wish to bring together Biography work (a process of personal discovery and development) and the adventure of travel. We can to tailor journeys to particular requests and groups.\n\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Text\" background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\"]\n\nJuliette was born in Morocco, having left for France, with her family, in her teens. Each time she returns there she finds a renewed discovery of her people and native culture. Larry brings his intimate relationship to Morocco into this: he first got a nose for leather in Fes, before taking up working with it for a quarter of a century; over the past 9 years he has been trading directly with fine craftsmen there. Add a life-long love of travel, teaching and Adult Learning and you have the ideal hosts.\n\nOur last organised journey was in 2012, the next is likely to be later in 2016. We are always interested in exploring ideas and requests for further Journeys, so if you would like any further information, or to receive news of future Journeys, please contact us with your details.\nCall Larry Leighton on 01453 755370 or use <a href=\"/contact\">the contact form</a>.\n\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section admin_label=\"Section\" fullwidth=\"off\" specialty=\"off\" transparent_background=\"off\" background_color=\"#ffffff\" allow_player_pause=\"off\" inner_shadow=\"off\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"off\" padding_mobile=\"off\" make_fullwidth=\"off\" use_custom_width=\"off\" width_unit=\"on\" make_equal=\"off\" use_custom_gutter=\"off\" module_id=\"contact\"][et_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\"][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Title: Opening Times\" background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\"]\n\n<h1>Opening Times</h1>\n\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\"][et_pb_column type=\"1_3\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Opening times text\" background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\"]\n\nThe Golden Fleece Warehouse is open every Friday and Saturday\nfrom 11.00 am to 5.30 pm\n\nFind us at:\nUnit 16D &amp; E,\nGriffin Mill,\nLondon Rd. Thrupp,\nStroud, GL5 2AZ\n(opposite Bailleys Paints)\n\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"2_3\"][et_pb_map admin_label=\"Map\" /][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section admin_label=\"Section\" fullwidth=\"off\" specialty=\"off\" transparent_background=\"off\" background_color=\"#ffffff\" allow_player_pause=\"off\" inner_shadow=\"off\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"off\" padding_mobile=\"off\" make_fullwidth=\"off\" use_custom_width=\"off\" width_unit=\"on\" make_equal=\"off\" use_custom_gutter=\"off\" module_id=\"contact\"][et_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\"][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Title: Contact\" background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\"]\n\n<h1>Contact</h1>\n\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section]','Golden Fleece Trading Company','','inherit','closed','closed','','4-autosave-v1','','','2016-04-19 20:33:28','2016-04-19 20:33:28','',4,'http://gft.tthtesting.co.uk/index.php/2016/04/19/4-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
